cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper deals with image generation and view synthesis, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The use of a novel network structure and training approach also suggests a potential contribution to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the evaluation of the approach on both synthetic and real examples suggests a potential application in multimedia (cs.MM).
